              resilience, and self-discovery.
            </p>
            <p class="featured-section-text">
              Her books have touched the hearts of readers around the world, and her unique voice continues to
              shine in the literary world. Discover her stories and immerse yourself in tales that leave a
              lasting impact.
            </p>
            <p class="featured-section-text">
